as.description: The element or component this component should render as. Can be overwrite by asChild
as.description_zh: 此组件应呈现为的元素或组件。可以被 asChild 覆盖

asChild.description: Change the default rendered element for the one passed as a child, merging their props and behavior.
asChild.description_zh: 更改作为子元素传递的默认渲染元素，合并其道具和行为。

invert.description: A unique value that inverts the component.
invert.description_zh: 一个独特的值,可以反转组件.

orientation.description: Orientation of the component. Either `vertical` or `horizontal`. Defaults to `horizontal`.
orientation.description_zh: 组件的方向.可以是 `vertical` 或 `horizontal`.默认为 `horizontal`.

decorative.description: Whether or not the component is purely decorative. When `true`, accessibility-related attributes are updated so that the rendered element is removed from the accessibility tree.
decorative.description_zh: 组件是否纯粹是装饰性的。当 `true` 时,相关的可访问性属性会更新,以便从可访问性树中移除渲染的元素.
